metadata.name: Unravel People's CLONEX
metadata.description: Abbreviation for unravel people's CLONEX, which represents an inactive state of pCLONEX. Users can participate in a new CloneX acquirement subscription and will receive unravel people's CLONEX as credit. upCLONEX can be claimed into pCLONEX when the subscription successfully acquires a new CloneX
